PRPO I wanted to address a post I saw earlier today from someone claiming this was a scam I admit initially I was also suspicious of this company The company IMO seemed like another Theranos I addressed my concerns about the 99 claim to them and they called me personally to discuss scientific reasoning Still I wanted to see research and they did say they were updating website to include that Today I noticed that the scientific research data is available and I did I also wanted to check is who from the scientific community was associated with the company This was the key for me Dr Sklar is a tenured faculty at Yale University Dr Makrigiorgos is a Professor of Radiation Oncology and Director of the Medical Physics Biophysics division at Dana Farber Cancer Institute Gil Mor MD PhD is a tenured at Yale University Dr Amin coauthored the 2002 World Health Organization WHO classification systems for urothelial tumors and renal neoplasms So many positives
